
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/884934/does-linuxs-splice2-work-when-splicing-from-a-tcp-socket

Linux has had support for splicing from a TCP socket since 2.6.25

so if you're using an earlier version, you're out of luck

our servers' version is 2.6.18, so we could not splicing from TCP socket now.



